WEBVTT

00:00:00.496 --> 00:00:02.405
Veoma mi je drago što sam danas ovde

00:00:02.405 --> 00:00:04.959
da bih govorio kako
bismo mogli popraviti

00:00:04.959 --> 00:00:06.995
oštećen mozak.

00:00:06.995 --> 00:00:09.237
Tim područjem sam izuzetno oduševljen

00:00:09.237 --> 00:00:11.722
jer kao neurolog,

00:00:11.722 --> 00:00:13.523
verujem da nudi sjajan način

00:00:13.523 --> 00:00:15.455
kojim bismo mogli ponuditi nadu

00:00:15.455 --> 00:00:18.028
pacijentima koji danas žive sa razornim

00:00:18.028 --> 00:00:21.986
i neizlečivim bolestima mozga.

00:00:21.986 --> 00:00:24.076
Evo ovde je problem.

00:00:24.076 --> 00:00:26.876
Tu možete da vidite sliku nečijeg mozga

00:00:26.876 --> 00:00:28.408
s Alchajmerovom bolešću

00:00:28.408 --> 00:00:30.327
pored zdravog mozga.